import React from 'react'
import { Typography } from '@mui/material'
const Description = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Typography variant="h3" component="h3" align="left" ml={2}>
        About me
      </Typography>
      <Typography variant="h5" component="h5" align="left" ml={5}>
        About me
      </Typography>
    </>
  )
}
export default Description
